                                    <%= x.FirstName%>
                                </h5>
                                <a href="/question/<%= x.qid%>"> <img src="https://www.situationalcommunication.com/app/uploads/2015/11/The-Answer-698x428-e1445614683535.jpg" style="width:10vw;height:5vw; text-align: right;"></a>

